<img src="http://orange-papers.info/orange-hen.jpg" border="2" height="138" width="122"></a>
<p>(She introduced Bill W. to
<br>Anne and Dr. Bob Smith in 1935.)</center>
</font></td>

<td>
<font size="4" base="4" face="Times,Roman">
<center><a href="orange-HenLtr09.jpg">
