<br>Click on envelope to magnify</center>
</font></td>

<td>
<font size="4" base="4" face="Times,Roman">
<center>To Clarence H. Snyder
<br>"The Home Brewmeister"
<br>in the story section of
<br>the big book
<br>
<a href="orange-chs.jpg">
<img src="http://orange-papers.info/orange-chs.jpg" border="2" height="142" width="100"></a>
